Visit PancakeSwap and click on “Connect” at the top right. Connect either your MetaMask or TrustWallet.

Step 2. Add SpaceDog

Add the SPACED token to your wallet using the following contract address: 0x227dfdaf28074078edb15e56adf58d2d925bc770

Step 3. Swap BEP-20 Token like a BNB to SPACED

Input your desired amount of BNB you want to exchange for SPACED. Then click ``Swap``. Select the gear icon and increase the slippage to 10-13%. Please also ensure you’re using V2 and have enough Binance Smart Chain to cover the transaction fees.

4. Be safe in the space.

Join the community, purchase SpaceDog and enjoy investing while the MRP is assessing the risk for you.

What is SpaceDog?

In a scam-ridden environment, finding opportunities to invest early on has become increasingly risky for investors. Not only is opening positions in new coins extremely dangerous because of the severe market volatility, but also because so-called projects are using several tactics to outright steal money from people. Rugpulls, timelocks, honeypot scams and organized team dumping are some of the problems several investors are encountering.
Imagine being able to track fresh new tokens immediately even before they launch while being sure if buying them is safe.
